---
title: Everything Bagel Breakfast Pizzas Serves 2 | with Smoked Salmon and Cream Cheese
description: In this brunch special  we took a brunch favourite and turned it into a pizza. Your new favourite pizza that is! Say hello to a thick schmear of cream cheese spread, everything bagel seasoning, smoked salmon, pickled shallots and capers, on all a delicious slice of 'za.
